WEBVTT

01:32.070 --> 01:34.950
[How dare you!?]

01:35.030 --> 01:37.979
[Episode 6]

01:44.840 --> 01:45.950
How dare you!

01:47.350 --> 01:48.150
Your Majesty!

01:48.150 --> 01:48.950
Your Majesty!

01:49.350 --> 01:51.479
Your Majesty,
I'm only doing this for Great Xia!

01:51.479 --> 01:52.710
Even if it may displease you,

01:52.710 --> 01:53.870
I must speak up!

01:54.789 --> 01:55.830
Th—That's right!

01:56.229 --> 01:57.759
I am willing to die to make my point!

01:57.759 --> 01:58.840
Me too!

02:04.480 --> 02:06.590
I wasn't talking about you.

02:07.070 --> 02:07.530
Come on.

02:08.000 --> 02:09.259
My beloved ministers,

02:09.750 --> 02:10.479
please rise.

02:11.190 --> 02:12.430
Get up.

02:12.590 --> 02:13.520
-Hurry.
-Get up.

02:13.520 --> 02:14.120
Up, up, up.

02:16.360 --> 02:17.760
Thank you, Your Majesty.

02:19.040 --> 02:20.710
Recently,
several of the Empress Dowager’s faction

02:20.710 --> 02:22.800
have submitted memorials
impeaching your father.

02:22.800 --> 02:25.460
I pretended to have a headache
to brush them off.

02:26.030 --> 02:29.360
It seems the Empress Dowager
means to make an example of him.

02:29.560 --> 02:30.620
Should we respond?

02:31.750 --> 02:32.740
We could.

02:33.310 --> 02:33.960
Just...

02:34.590 --> 02:35.250
demote him.

02:37.120 --> 02:38.680
That heartless?

02:39.190 --> 02:40.320
It’s not heartless.

02:40.470 --> 02:41.670
It's for his own good.

02:42.150 --> 02:43.030
How so?

02:43.590 --> 02:45.150
On the surface, they’re impeaching him.

02:45.150 --> 02:45.840
In truth,

02:46.310 --> 02:48.240
the Empress Dowager is warning me.

02:48.870 --> 02:51.150
After all, the incident of
Noble Consort Wei losing the sarira agate

02:51.150 --> 02:52.550
escalated because of me.

02:52.910 --> 02:54.590
If she doesn’t vent her anger,

02:55.520 --> 02:57.050
this nominal father of mine

02:57.310 --> 02:58.800
may suffer far worse.

03:01.710 --> 03:03.520
Then we can't just demote your father.

03:03.520 --> 03:06.240
I should probably give you
the cold shoulder for a while too.

03:06.240 --> 03:07.770
We have to make it look real.

03:08.720 --> 03:10.320
CEO Dan, you’re meticulous.

03:14.710 --> 03:15.750
Minister Yu!

03:16.590 --> 03:17.990
How dare you!

03:18.590 --> 03:19.390
Your Majesty,

03:19.710 --> 03:20.079
I am

03:20.590 --> 03:22.390
wrongly accused, Your Majesty!

03:23.030 --> 03:23.829
Your Majesty!

03:23.960 --> 03:26.120
It’s true I enjoy playing cards

03:27.280 --> 03:29.280
and often gather with a few friends.

03:29.560 --> 03:29.960
But...

03:30.280 --> 03:32.230
accusing me of taking bribes

03:32.470 --> 03:33.750
is simply false!

03:34.310 --> 03:37.310
I’m just better at cards than most,

03:37.840 --> 03:39.820
so winning a bit more is normal.

03:40.240 --> 03:40.770
However,

03:40.800 --> 03:41.960
the game I play

03:42.030 --> 03:43.690
is 10 coins a round,

03:43.870 --> 03:46.130
with a daily cap
of half a string of coins!

03:46.280 --> 03:47.079
How...

03:47.710 --> 03:48.510
How could that

03:48.840 --> 03:51.500
possibly count as taking bribes,
Your Majesty?

03:51.680 --> 03:53.190
How dare you keep making excuses!

03:53.190 --> 03:55.750
If only one person impeached you,
you could claim injustice.

03:55.750 --> 03:57.680
But now 3 court ministers
are impeaching you together,

03:57.680 --> 03:59.120
with evidence to back it up!

03:59.120 --> 04:00.710
How can you argue your way out of this?

04:00.710 --> 04:01.170
Guards!

04:02.560 --> 04:03.240
Take off his official hat!

04:03.240 --> 04:03.560
Yes!

04:05.280 --> 04:06.680
It’s already fallen off.

04:08.840 --> 04:10.640
Then demote him and dock his pay!

04:10.910 --> 04:11.370
Get out!

04:12.280 --> 04:13.080
Your Majesty!

04:13.630 --> 04:14.430
Your Majesty!

04:14.630 --> 04:14.910
I...

04:15.240 --> 04:17.480
I am innocent, Your Majesty!

04:17.720 --> 04:20.480
Your Majesty, I am innocent!

04:21.630 --> 04:22.430
Your Majesty,

04:22.830 --> 04:24.370
for my sake,

04:24.560 --> 04:26.200
please spare my father!

04:26.480 --> 04:27.790
You dare plead for him?

04:28.600 --> 04:30.220
If I spare Minister Yu,

04:31.000 --> 04:33.060
how will the court officials view me?

04:33.470 --> 04:36.370
And how do I answer to the people?

04:43.390 --> 04:44.120
My father...

04:45.040 --> 04:46.770
My father only gambles for fun.

04:47.120 --> 04:48.900
He never took bribes!

04:49.310 --> 04:50.510
Stop making excuses!

04:50.510 --> 04:51.640
Between officials,

04:51.800 --> 04:53.560
there is no such thing
as gambling for fun!

04:53.560 --> 04:54.290
Well then...

04:54.680 --> 04:55.610
have some aorta.

04:57.950 --> 04:58.300
Here.

04:58.800 --> 05:00.060
Have some vegetables.

05:00.070 --> 05:01.470
You’ve got mouth ulcers.

05:02.870 --> 05:03.670
Your Majesty,

05:04.120 --> 05:07.320
are you really unwilling to show me
even a bit of leniency?

05:07.950 --> 05:09.500
I’ve already shown plenty.

05:09.950 --> 05:11.480
Otherwise, how would that old man

05:11.480 --> 05:12.670
still be alive?

05:12.870 --> 05:13.920
Kneeling won’t help!

05:13.920 --> 05:16.450
Go back to your Zhaoyang Palace
immediately!

05:16.630 --> 05:17.640
I'm not full yet.

05:17.800 --> 05:18.860
Say two more lines.

05:19.120 --> 05:20.390
Any more and it's just filler dialogue.

05:20.390 --> 05:21.360
Just pad it a bit.

05:25.720 --> 05:27.500
You’re heartless, cold,

05:27.710 --> 05:29.310
and completely unreasonable!

05:29.310 --> 05:31.040
How dare you call me heartless,

05:31.190 --> 05:31.900
cold,

05:32.430 --> 05:33.490
and unreasonable?

05:34.430 --> 05:35.560
Then answer me this.

05:35.600 --> 05:36.970
How am I heartless,

05:37.190 --> 05:37.720
cold,

05:38.310 --> 05:39.680
and unreasonable?

05:40.390 --> 05:42.270
Your Majesty, please calm your anger!

05:42.270 --> 05:45.190
I will never do it again!

05:45.240 --> 05:47.000
If there's a next time,

05:47.600 --> 05:49.330
I’ll wipe out your entire clan!

05:53.040 --> 05:54.800
I honestly can't keep up
with your performance.

05:54.800 --> 05:55.860
Let's call it a day.

05:58.070 --> 05:58.670
No, no, no!

05:59.240 --> 06:01.300
It's worth half my lifetime’s wages.

06:01.800 --> 06:03.460
No matter how expensive it is,

06:03.750 --> 06:05.080
can you take it with you?

06:08.040 --> 06:10.950
[Bilan Pavilion]

06:08.560 --> 06:09.420
Have you heard?

06:09.680 --> 06:11.210
His Majesty flew into a rage

06:11.390 --> 06:13.560
and kicked Consort Yu
straight out of his bedchamber,

06:13.560 --> 06:15.600
all the way to the palace gate.

06:17.310 --> 06:19.510
She has completely lost face.

06:20.360 --> 06:23.160
Does His Majesty really have
that kind of strength?

06:23.160 --> 06:24.160
Of course he does.

06:24.560 --> 06:26.090
I also heard that Consort Yu

06:26.120 --> 06:28.430
stayed at the palace gate
and refused to leave,

06:28.430 --> 06:30.720
begging nonstop for her gambler father.

06:31.270 --> 06:32.870
In a fit of anger, His Majesty

06:33.000 --> 06:34.570
almost had her executed.

06:37.000 --> 06:39.140
Sisters, where did you hear all this?

06:39.430 --> 06:40.140
Is it true?

06:40.240 --> 06:41.770
Oh, my silly little sister.

06:41.830 --> 06:43.000
I don't know about other things,

06:43.000 --> 06:44.590
but no one gathers gossips

06:44.750 --> 06:47.480
better than Concubine He
and Concubine Chu.

06:49.630 --> 06:50.950
Your Majesty!

06:52.070 --> 06:53.120
Your Majesty!

06:53.430 --> 06:55.310
Why are you so heartless?

06:56.360 --> 06:57.000
That is my father

06:57.000 --> 07:00.310
who gave birth to me, raised me,
and taught me everything!

07:01.120 --> 07:02.460
This time, Consort Yu

07:02.750 --> 07:04.000
is done for.

07:04.190 --> 07:06.240
She's doomed.

07:06.430 --> 07:07.720
Then...

07:08.030 --> 07:09.360
what are we waiting for?

07:10.720 --> 07:11.560
Sisters,

07:12.000 --> 07:14.260
since ancient times they’ve always said
that beauty brings ruin to nations.

07:14.260 --> 07:17.190
It refers to people like Noble Consort Wei
and Noble Consort Yu.

07:17.190 --> 07:18.480
Some rely on family background,

07:18.480 --> 07:19.640
others on beauty.

07:19.830 --> 07:22.430
But they only bewitched His Majesty
for a moment.

07:22.430 --> 07:24.360
And what kind of man is His Majesty?

07:24.430 --> 07:28.220
He cares for the realm
and holds all the people in his heart.

07:28.360 --> 07:30.360
How could he be so easily bewitched?

07:30.830 --> 07:32.070
As consorts, we must not imitate

07:32.070 --> 07:34.800
those demonic consorts
who bewitch their ruler.

07:34.950 --> 07:38.240
Instead, we should keep Great Xia in our hearts and share His Majesty’s burdens.

07:38.240 --> 07:39.370
Am I right, Sisters?

07:41.120 --> 07:42.180
Where is everyone?

07:42.270 --> 07:44.270
They all went
to share His Majesty’s burdens.

07:44.270 --> 07:45.390
Wait for me!

07:45.250 --> 07:48.290
[Bilan Pavilion]

07:46.510 --> 07:47.430
Wait for me!

07:47.600 --> 07:48.460
I'm coming too!

07:50.560 --> 07:51.760
With the likes of you,

07:53.120 --> 07:54.720
how can you compete with her?

08:04.800 --> 08:05.600
Your Majesty.

08:08.070 --> 08:09.470
Consort Shu just came by.

08:09.720 --> 08:11.160
Fearing she might disturb your rest,

08:11.160 --> 08:13.890
I had her tell me about
what happened to Consort Yu

08:14.230 --> 08:15.230
and sent her away.

08:16.830 --> 08:17.800
His Majesty dealt with

08:17.800 --> 08:19.240
Minister Yu so swiftly?

08:20.240 --> 08:20.830
I really

08:21.270 --> 08:22.680
didn’t expect it.

08:23.390 --> 08:25.390
What is there to be surprised about?

08:26.920 --> 08:29.510
A caged canary—

08:30.120 --> 08:31.560
once released,

08:32.030 --> 08:33.690
can it really fly up to the sky?

08:34.720 --> 08:35.520
You're right.

08:36.120 --> 08:37.120
Consort Yu indeed

08:37.600 --> 08:38.870
made a huge scene because of it.

08:38.870 --> 08:41.260
His Majesty scolded her harshly

08:41.510 --> 08:43.110
and kicked her out in the end.

08:46.200 --> 08:48.120
She’s too inexperienced.

08:49.080 --> 08:50.790
So short-sighted.

08:51.080 --> 08:52.410
She doesn’t understand

08:52.600 --> 08:54.870
how quickly a ruler’s heart can change.

08:55.200 --> 08:55.930
Yes, indeed.

09:00.910 --> 09:02.630
This Consort Shu,

09:03.480 --> 09:05.480
however, has real insight.

09:06.390 --> 09:09.720
Have her come to pay her respects to me
within the next few days.

09:09.720 --> 09:10.080
Yes.

09:12.910 --> 09:13.710
Your Majesty,

09:14.240 --> 09:16.900
Lord Mu
has been waiting outside for a long time.

09:17.150 --> 09:18.120
Let him in now.

09:22.030 --> 09:23.910
Greetings, Your Majesty.

09:24.000 --> 09:24.960
Mr. Mu,

09:25.960 --> 09:28.000
how did you come up with that idea?

09:28.910 --> 09:30.630
Mr. Mu

09:30.870 --> 09:32.630
is remarkably sharp.

09:34.030 --> 09:35.360
How did he know

09:35.720 --> 09:37.780
that Minister Yu loves to play cards?

09:38.150 --> 09:41.000
This is truly killing two birds
with one stone.

09:43.120 --> 09:44.120
The plan

09:44.440 --> 09:46.480
seems perfectly logical.

09:46.790 --> 09:49.200
It pleased me greatly.

09:50.790 --> 09:52.190
Thank you, Your Majesty.

09:52.510 --> 09:54.910
I only offered a small strategy.

09:55.870 --> 09:58.510
It was all thanks to
Consort Shu’s brother.

09:59.360 --> 10:01.360
The few words he spoke in court

10:02.080 --> 10:03.630
proved crucial.

10:04.270 --> 10:06.270
Not only did every word hit the mark,

10:06.720 --> 10:10.520
but they also blocked any possibility
of His Majesty showing mercy.

10:11.960 --> 10:13.270
Good.

10:14.600 --> 10:16.030
Useful people like him

10:16.440 --> 10:18.600
must be heavily rewarded.

10:20.080 --> 10:21.480
Thank you, Your Majesty.

10:21.910 --> 10:22.440
I

10:23.000 --> 10:24.260
will take my leave now.

10:32.080 --> 10:32.880
Your Majesty,

10:33.360 --> 10:35.240
I'll go prepare the rewards now.

10:39.840 --> 10:41.390
Rewards?

10:42.550 --> 10:44.790
To be able to serve me

10:45.150 --> 10:47.790
is the greatest reward of all.

10:49.790 --> 10:51.200
You are too honest.

10:53.840 --> 10:54.390
Look.

10:55.150 --> 10:56.960
These 3 little birds

10:56.960 --> 10:59.670
are becoming brighter and brighter.

11:03.600 --> 11:05.330
How did the Minister of Revenue

11:05.390 --> 11:06.390
die?

11:09.790 --> 11:10.720
And who arrested

11:11.360 --> 11:12.360
Grand Tutor Wei?

11:14.630 --> 11:16.230
As for General Luo's son,

11:17.550 --> 11:19.810
if he didn’t want him to enter the palace,

11:21.720 --> 11:23.320
could he really not stop him?

11:27.630 --> 11:29.690
The knife was handed to him by others,

11:30.480 --> 11:32.080
but whether he takes it or not

11:35.270 --> 11:37.720
ultimately depends on His Majesty’s will.

11:38.960 --> 11:40.480
His Highness, you mean...

11:40.960 --> 11:42.390
Our Emperor

11:43.840 --> 11:46.480
has always been unpredictable.

11:48.750 --> 11:51.720
Still, I must remind you all

11:52.840 --> 11:55.670
not to be fooled by his mad-king facade.

11:59.150 --> 12:00.080
Especially now,

12:02.150 --> 12:03.480
in this palace,

12:05.670 --> 12:07.750
he is no longer alone.

12:21.600 --> 12:23.530
Ever since the fire at the library,

12:25.910 --> 12:28.270
His Highness
has not entered the palace again.

12:28.270 --> 12:29.910
I went to inquire at his residence.

12:29.910 --> 12:31.150
They only said

12:31.200 --> 12:33.030
His Highness
has been busy with official duties.

12:33.030 --> 12:34.750
I then asked whether His Highness

12:34.750 --> 12:37.010
had seen the letter in the brocade pouch,

12:37.270 --> 12:38.530
and they gave no reply.

12:43.960 --> 12:46.690
Your Highness,
with Consort Yu’s father demoted

12:47.080 --> 12:48.000
and she herself

12:48.000 --> 12:49.930
fallen out of His Majesty's favor,

12:50.000 --> 12:51.240
all other consorts

12:51.300 --> 12:54.000
are doing everything they can
to vie for His Majesty’s attention.

12:54.000 --> 12:55.200
Let them fight for it.

12:56.600 --> 12:57.390
I don't care.

13:00.720 --> 13:02.200
Yu Wanyin was right.

13:03.170 --> 13:03.910
Here,

13:05.090 --> 13:07.150
a man can lift you to the heavens today

13:08.630 --> 13:10.430
and cast you into hell tomorrow.

13:11.440 --> 13:13.840
Their love and hate
are but a fleeting whim.

13:14.790 --> 13:15.650
Your Highness.

13:19.790 --> 13:22.390
Your Highness,
Eunuch An is here with a decree.

13:34.840 --> 13:35.790
Concubine Xie.

13:37.120 --> 13:40.720
His Majesty decrees
that
Concubine Xie is to attend him tonight.

13:41.540 --> 13:43.470
Congratulations, Your Highness.

13:43.670 --> 13:44.360
What?

13:45.250 --> 13:46.910
He wants me to attend him tonight?

13:46.910 --> 13:47.440
What?

13:48.200 --> 13:49.270
Let her attend me?

13:49.670 --> 13:50.030
Yes.

13:52.200 --> 13:54.210
You want me to find another woman...

13:54.480 --> 13:55.800
to serve me in bed?

13:57.510 --> 13:58.270
Keep it down.

13:58.480 --> 13:59.670
What's going on inside?

13:59.670 --> 14:02.080
His Majesty and Noble Consort Yu
seem to have a quarrel.

14:02.080 --> 14:02.900
A quarrel?

14:06.270 --> 14:09.730
Why does it feel like I'm forcing
a good boy into prostitution?

14:12.080 --> 14:14.120
It's not like she'll actually
serve you in bed.

14:14.120 --> 14:15.000
I just figured out

14:15.000 --> 14:17.260
how to get the list of scholars
out of her.

14:17.960 --> 14:18.480
Mr. Bei.

14:20.270 --> 14:20.750
Mr. Bei.

14:21.720 --> 14:23.240
You've roamed the world for so long

14:23.240 --> 14:25.040
and lived among the common folk.

14:25.150 --> 14:26.350
Do you know of any drug

14:26.440 --> 14:28.440
that can make someone hallucinate?

14:28.910 --> 14:30.200
You want to drug Dan?

14:31.240 --> 14:32.040
No, no.

14:32.470 --> 14:34.000
How could I do that to CEO...

14:35.530 --> 14:37.470
I am using it for a proper purpose.

14:38.200 --> 14:40.000
I need someone to tell the truth.

14:40.100 --> 14:40.790
Simple.

14:41.270 --> 14:42.490
Get him drunk.

14:43.240 --> 14:43.670
Right.

14:45.200 --> 14:46.600
Drink makes people talk.

14:49.510 --> 14:51.080
But what if she remembers everything

14:51.080 --> 14:52.550
the next morning?

14:53.080 --> 14:54.390
That’s even easier.

14:55.440 --> 14:56.570
Make her drink more.

14:59.630 --> 15:02.550
You know I speed-read the book,

15:02.720 --> 15:04.480
so I don't remember the scholars' names
at all.

15:04.480 --> 15:05.720
But Xie Yong'er does.

15:06.600 --> 15:07.550
She went through the entire

15:07.550 --> 15:10.840
"A thousand trees blossoms at night
in the East" carefully.

15:10.840 --> 15:12.240
When those talented and virtuous scholars

15:12.240 --> 15:13.200
died unjustly,

15:13.670 --> 15:15.150
it was truly heartbreaking.

15:15.150 --> 15:17.270
It must have made a deep impression
on her.

15:17.270 --> 15:19.400
And when the next imperial exam comes,

15:19.480 --> 15:23.120
the list of candidates Prince Duan
is going to poach will come from her.

15:23.120 --> 15:24.360
Stop grunting.

15:24.630 --> 15:25.390
Why don’t you...

15:25.390 --> 15:26.520
think it over again?

15:31.120 --> 15:33.320
Besides,
I’ve already acted without consulting you

15:33.320 --> 15:34.920
and had Eunuch An notify her.

15:36.200 --> 15:36.600
You...

15:37.390 --> 15:38.720
So, for the greater good,

15:38.720 --> 15:40.050
make a small sacrifice.

15:46.910 --> 15:47.910
Where’s the wine?

15:50.630 --> 15:52.390
Mr. Bei prepared 2 jars
of the strongest stuff.

15:52.390 --> 15:54.200
You’d better make sure it works.

15:55.150 --> 15:55.790
I'll try my best.

15:55.790 --> 15:56.360
Try?

15:57.480 --> 15:58.340
I guarantee it.

15:58.720 --> 15:59.150
A 100%

15:59.560 --> 16:00.220
guarantee.

16:07.210 --> 16:08.410
Why is he angry?

16:10.720 --> 16:11.670
Eunuch An, eat more.

16:11.670 --> 16:12.330
Delicious.

16:12.790 --> 16:13.270
Try this.

16:13.170 --> 16:21.270
[Zhaoyang Hall]

16:13.440 --> 16:14.170
It's not bad.

16:15.200 --> 16:15.730
Try mine.

16:15.960 --> 16:16.360
Good, right?

16:16.360 --> 16:17.020
Delicious.

16:17.240 --> 16:17.700
Not bad.

16:20.600 --> 16:21.400
Your Majesty.

16:22.480 --> 16:23.610
Go back to my palace!

16:24.600 --> 16:25.510
Depart!

16:26.600 --> 16:27.410
Stop eating! Hurry!

16:27.410 --> 16:30.310
[Zhaoyang Hall]

16:30.790 --> 16:31.320
Hurry up!

16:33.510 --> 16:35.000
This Xiahou Dan...

16:35.870 --> 16:37.400
When did he become so weird?

16:39.440 --> 16:40.700
Was it at Banyue House?

16:42.440 --> 16:43.440
Or even earlier?

16:45.170 --> 16:47.240
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

16:47.520 --> 16:48.760
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

16:49.110 --> 16:51.270
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

16:49.720 --> 16:52.000
Is this the legendary
Suspension Bridge Effect?

16:51.630 --> 16:53.010
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

16:53.100 --> 16:55.400
♪ Words unspoken ♪

16:53.270 --> 16:54.030
If one of us

16:54.030 --> 16:55.630
has to be a love-struck fool,

16:56.150 --> 16:57.670
it shouldn’t be Xiahou Dan.

16:57.020 --> 16:59.400
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

16:58.320 --> 17:01.050
Am I just flattering myself
and overthinking it?

17:01.140 --> 17:03.230
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

17:03.620 --> 17:04.710
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

17:05.160 --> 17:07.079
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

17:07.640 --> 17:08.970
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

17:09.099 --> 17:11.510
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

17:13.099 --> 17:16.540
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

17:16.990 --> 17:20.490
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

17:20.349 --> 17:21.510
Yu Wanyin, oh Yu Wanyin.

17:21.060 --> 17:24.060
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

17:21.920 --> 17:22.750
Sober up.

17:23.000 --> 17:24.520
Don't be a love-struck fool.

17:24.520 --> 17:26.450
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

17:25.880 --> 17:26.650
He cares about you

17:26.650 --> 17:28.250
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

17:28.069 --> 17:29.880
because this is a survival game,

17:28.590 --> 17:30.200
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

17:30.600 --> 17:32.700
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

17:31.200 --> 17:32.730
and you’ve read the script,

17:33.110 --> 17:34.480
which makes you more valuable
than the others.

17:33.120 --> 17:36.280
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

17:37.070 --> 17:38.510
He’s only forced
to form a closer bond with you

17:37.070 --> 17:39.480
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

17:39.550 --> 17:40.610
♪ Still unchanged ♪

17:39.880 --> 17:41.960
to survive dangerous situations.

17:41.160 --> 17:44.020
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

17:44.620 --> 17:46.070
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

17:46.180 --> 17:50.720
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

17:53.440 --> 17:54.240
Your Majesty.

17:54.510 --> 17:55.310
Your Majesty!

17:55.360 --> 17:56.160
Your Majesty!

17:57.920 --> 17:58.620
Hurry!

17:59.200 --> 17:59.600
Hurry!

18:00.440 --> 18:00.840
Hurry!

18:04.550 --> 18:05.030
Why are you...

18:04.990 --> 18:08.520
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

18:07.550 --> 18:09.030
I can summon her to serve me,

18:09.030 --> 18:10.840
but you must stay by my side
the whole time.

18:09.060 --> 18:12.060
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

18:11.110 --> 18:12.600
You’re not allowed to leave.

18:12.600 --> 18:14.450
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

18:12.790 --> 18:13.590
Do you hear me?

18:14.670 --> 18:16.350
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

18:16.650 --> 18:18.320
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

18:18.610 --> 18:20.770
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

18:21.150 --> 18:24.330
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

18:22.750 --> 18:23.880
Why are you smiling?

18:25.130 --> 18:27.540
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

18:25.550 --> 18:26.230
Don't worry,

18:26.230 --> 18:26.690
CEO Dan.

18:27.660 --> 18:28.710
♪ Still unchanged ♪

18:27.720 --> 18:29.450
We're in the same boat.

18:29.170 --> 18:32.080
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

18:29.880 --> 18:31.210
I'll help you to the end.

18:32.630 --> 18:34.080
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

18:34.140 --> 18:41.490
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

18:57.480 --> 18:58.240
Am I really

18:59.110 --> 19:00.510
going to serve him in bed?

19:02.440 --> 19:04.510
With a man I don’t love at all?

19:07.240 --> 19:08.310
And the one I do love

19:08.310 --> 19:11.770
stays distant, drifting in and out of reach
with no word at all.

19:13.480 --> 19:15.410
Why is it that even with the script,

19:15.510 --> 19:17.640
I still can’t control my own life?

19:19.240 --> 19:21.700
Then does everything
I’ve been fighting for

19:21.830 --> 19:23.160
truly mean anything?

19:25.720 --> 19:26.640
Your Highness,

19:26.920 --> 19:27.650
please go in.

19:27.750 --> 19:29.480
His Majesty is waiting inside.

19:51.960 --> 19:53.420
Greetings, Your Majesty.

19:55.590 --> 19:56.120
Drink up.

19:57.720 --> 19:58.720
So direct?

19:59.110 --> 20:00.350
No finesse at all?

20:21.070 --> 20:21.930
Keep drinking.

20:36.480 --> 20:37.740
Drink from the bottle.

21:02.480 --> 21:03.640
What’s 1 plus 3?

21:06.830 --> 21:07.400
4.

21:07.400 --> 21:08.990
What about 46 plus 31?

21:09.160 --> 21:09.680
77.

21:09.680 --> 21:11.640
426 plus 674?

21:11.680 --> 21:12.160
1,100.

21:12.350 --> 21:13.510
How did she calculate that?

21:13.510 --> 21:14.030
So fast.

21:14.590 --> 21:16.390
You can really hold your liquor.

21:18.030 --> 21:19.690
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

21:21.310 --> 21:22.840
Eunuch An, bring more wine!

21:28.270 --> 21:29.470
I will drink with you.

21:30.210 --> 21:31.860
Drink while you can.

21:32.350 --> 21:33.950
Don't let life wear you away.

21:34.350 --> 21:34.860
My dear,

21:35.310 --> 21:35.970
bottoms up.

21:36.310 --> 21:38.220
Good days pass, bad days pass.

21:38.480 --> 21:40.400
All I ask is to stay in a good mood.

21:41.310 --> 21:42.550
Your Majesty, cheers.

21:42.550 --> 21:44.550
With a kindred spirit,
a thousand cups aren’t enough.

21:44.550 --> 21:45.960
Tonight, don’t even think about

21:45.960 --> 21:47.020
dodging the drink.

21:47.240 --> 21:49.510
You don’t get drunk like this very often.

21:50.000 --> 21:51.830
Who cares what’s right or wrong?

21:51.830 --> 21:53.830
If you don’t drink and I don’t drink,

21:54.110 --> 21:55.640
what’s the palace wine for?

21:55.750 --> 21:58.150
If you don’t get drunk
and I don’t get drunk,

21:59.000 --> 22:00.400
the tyrant’s bed...

22:01.680 --> 22:02.740
I can't sleep in it.

22:04.270 --> 22:04.840
What?

22:05.790 --> 22:07.650
I didn't ask you to serve me in bed.

22:14.310 --> 22:14.920
My dear?

22:15.440 --> 22:15.900
My dear?

22:16.550 --> 22:17.780
What is 1 plus 3?

22:18.110 --> 22:19.000
Are you crazy?

22:20.400 --> 22:21.730
Stop talking nonsense.

22:21.880 --> 22:22.540
Just drink!

22:31.000 --> 22:32.730
Come out. She’s cursing me now.

22:33.270 --> 22:35.000
Looks like she’s drunk enough.

22:45.240 --> 22:46.110
Ma Chunchun.

22:47.790 --> 22:48.850
Who is Ma Chunchun?

22:49.720 --> 22:51.450
It's her real name in the novel.

22:51.590 --> 22:52.440
Who is it?

22:53.110 --> 22:54.770
You messed with my storyline,

22:55.110 --> 22:56.570
and you're asking who I am?

22:56.680 --> 22:58.110
You know my name.

23:00.310 --> 23:01.680
You know my name?

23:02.440 --> 23:03.880
So you must be Seven-Tailed Fox,

23:03.880 --> 23:06.790
the author of

23:07.590 --> 23:10.320
"A thousand trees blossoms at night
in the East."

23:13.160 --> 23:13.960
That's right.

23:16.400 --> 23:18.740
I never thought you'd enter my book

23:19.160 --> 23:20.440
and stir up trouble.

23:20.440 --> 23:21.500
How are my parents?

23:23.790 --> 23:24.590
They are fine.

23:27.160 --> 23:29.550
I never thought you'd transmigrate
into my book

23:29.550 --> 23:30.480
and stir up trouble.

23:30.480 --> 23:32.140
What place did my idol come in?

23:33.790 --> 23:35.790
The platform cancelled the voting.

23:37.110 --> 23:37.750
What place?

23:37.750 --> 23:39.810
Tell her something she wants to hear.

23:40.310 --> 23:41.040
First place.

23:41.200 --> 23:41.930
First place.

23:44.030 --> 23:45.200
Impossible.

23:45.200 --> 23:47.480
That platform is the worst.

23:49.550 --> 23:50.720
As a 2D character,

23:51.070 --> 23:53.870
isn't her character setting
a bit too fleshed out?

23:55.350 --> 23:58.440
My poor idol.

23:59.750 --> 24:00.480
My sweetheart!

24:00.480 --> 24:01.550
Alright, Ma Chunchun.

24:01.550 --> 24:03.070
Let's get down to business.

24:03.070 --> 24:04.130
I didn’t expect you

24:04.510 --> 24:06.070
to stir up so much trouble,

24:06.750 --> 24:08.610
completely deceive Prince Duan,

24:08.720 --> 24:10.260
and mess up

24:10.350 --> 24:11.750
the original storyline.

24:11.790 --> 24:13.350
How do you plan to take responsibility?

24:13.350 --> 24:15.510
If I follow your storyline,

24:15.680 --> 24:16.680
I’d just end up

24:17.640 --> 24:19.480
dying early as cannon fodder.

24:20.240 --> 24:20.880
But you shouldn't have

24:20.880 --> 24:22.640
leaked the names of those failed scholars

24:22.640 --> 24:23.640
to Prince Duan.

24:23.920 --> 24:25.680
That way they’d lose the chance
to be strengthened.

24:25.680 --> 24:26.210
Exactly.

24:27.480 --> 24:28.340
Strengthened?

24:35.750 --> 24:37.640
You call that strengthened?

24:38.270 --> 24:39.530
In the original story,

24:39.880 --> 24:41.930
after Li Yunxi and Yang Duojie

24:42.350 --> 24:44.640
exposed that rogue for cheating,

24:45.240 --> 24:46.640
they were beaten to death

24:47.200 --> 24:49.270
in sacks once they left the exam hall!

24:49.270 --> 24:49.960
Li Yunxi.

24:50.240 --> 24:51.030
And Er Lan.

24:52.110 --> 24:53.970
Er Lan disguised herself as a man.

24:54.200 --> 24:56.640
When she was discovered, she was assaulted

24:57.150 --> 24:59.080
and then kicked out of the capital.

24:59.240 --> 24:59.840
In the end,

25:00.590 --> 25:03.050
she killed herself in anger
and resentment.

25:03.790 --> 25:04.720
Killed herself?

25:04.830 --> 25:06.110
And Wang Zhao,

25:06.480 --> 25:07.160
Du Shan,

25:07.510 --> 25:08.790
Cen Jintian—

25:09.680 --> 25:12.430
you created them all.

25:14.000 --> 25:17.080
Why did you kill them off
with your own hands?

25:19.750 --> 25:20.550
That's right.

25:20.590 --> 25:21.190
It's them.

25:21.920 --> 25:23.320
If we find these talents,

25:24.240 --> 25:26.240
Yan millet yields will reach 1,800 per mu,

25:26.240 --> 25:27.740
with no fear of drought or inflation.

25:27.740 --> 25:29.040
[Li Yunxi][Yang Duojie][Expose]

25:28.110 --> 25:29.550
But these ambitious scholars

25:29.060 --> 25:30.470
[Wang Zhao][Du Shan][Cen Jintian]

25:30.070 --> 25:31.110
must hate the tyrant to the bone.

25:30.500 --> 25:31.590
[Erlan][Disguised as a man]

25:31.920 --> 25:34.450
That is why Prince Duan
was able to poach them.

25:36.350 --> 25:40.010
If I want to convince them to work for me
before the imperial exams,

25:41.030 --> 25:42.630
I need to come up with an idea.

25:43.590 --> 25:44.720
You damned author!

25:45.510 --> 25:46.040
I'm here!

25:47.880 --> 25:50.830
You've made me suffer so much.

25:52.440 --> 25:53.480
Alright, alright.

25:53.480 --> 25:54.280
It's okay now.

25:55.160 --> 25:56.240
Keep your voice down.

25:56.240 --> 25:57.790
There are people worse off than you.

25:57.790 --> 25:59.740
I don't care about anyone else's misery.

25:59.740 --> 26:02.200
[Li Yunxi, Yang Duojie, Wang Zhao,
Du Shan, Cen Jintian, Er Lan]

26:00.270 --> 26:01.310
I worked so hard,

26:02.510 --> 26:05.440
but why doesn’t Prince Duan trust me?

26:06.440 --> 26:08.300
I was the one who gave him the idea.

26:08.790 --> 26:11.190
I told him to poison
Deputy Commander Zhao,

26:12.030 --> 26:13.960
but in the end, he didn’t believe me

26:14.350 --> 26:16.480
and poisoned the guy's horse instead!

26:18.440 --> 26:19.370
What did you say?

26:19.550 --> 26:20.070
Yes,

26:20.440 --> 26:21.040
I admit it.

26:21.880 --> 26:23.740
His idea worked better than mine.

26:24.200 --> 26:26.720
But I was following your storyline.

26:27.110 --> 26:28.720
Why did he change the script?

26:29.590 --> 26:30.390
That's right.

26:31.720 --> 26:32.510
In the original story, Prince Duan

26:32.510 --> 26:34.370
did follow Xie Yong'er’s advice,

26:34.440 --> 26:35.640
using an aphrodisiac

26:35.750 --> 26:38.680
to get Deputy Commander Zhao to harass
the Imperial Guard Commander’s concubine,

26:38.680 --> 26:40.590
causing the two of them to become enemies.

26:40.590 --> 26:42.310
In the end, for self-preservation,
Deputy Commander Zhao

26:42.310 --> 26:44.170
allied himself with Prince Duan.

26:45.000 --> 26:45.400
But...

26:46.960 --> 26:48.360
why, in Xu Yao's records,

26:49.200 --> 26:50.530
is was a different plan?

26:51.400 --> 26:52.640
Invite Deputy Zhao to drink,

26:52.640 --> 26:53.640
poison his horse,

26:53.830 --> 26:56.110
and let the crazed horse trample the late Emperor’s ceremonial carriage set.

26:56.110 --> 26:59.440
That set was a gift bestowed on
Prince Duan by the late Emperor.

26:59.440 --> 27:01.000
Destroying an imperial gift
is a far graver crime

27:01.000 --> 27:03.240
than harassing a commander’s concubine,

27:03.240 --> 27:05.310
enough to frighten
Deputy Commander Zhao out of his wits.

27:05.310 --> 27:05.910
Could it be

27:06.590 --> 27:09.240
that Prince Duan
has deviated from the original script

27:09.240 --> 27:10.970
and developed a will of his own?

27:11.110 --> 27:13.000
And that wasn't the first time.

27:14.000 --> 27:14.800
If he

27:15.030 --> 27:16.550
never trusts me,

27:18.200 --> 27:19.580
then won’t I

27:20.920 --> 27:22.070
be useless to him?

27:26.440 --> 27:28.880
How am I supposed to change my fate then?

27:32.310 --> 27:33.240
-Wanyin.
-Something is wrong.

27:33.240 --> 27:34.440
I've thought of a way.

27:34.590 --> 27:35.350
Keep an eye on her.

27:35.350 --> 27:36.280
I need to go back.

27:39.270 --> 27:40.930
Without what happened today,

27:41.270 --> 27:42.270
I might never have noticed

27:42.270 --> 27:43.530
these subtle changes.

27:44.440 --> 27:45.240
Even if I had,

27:45.640 --> 27:47.720
I would’ve brushed them off
as faulty memory.

27:47.720 --> 27:49.580
If I hadn’t obtained Xu Yao’s book

27:50.000 --> 27:50.510
and had continued following the plot

27:50.510 --> 27:52.270
of Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort,

27:52.270 --> 27:54.470
directing Xiahou Dan to do rash things,

27:54.720 --> 27:56.980
we would have kept missing these details

27:57.480 --> 27:59.680
and eventually fallen into utter ruin.

28:14.500 --> 28:14.690
[Kill the imperial censor's
secret guards in the backyard]

28:14.690 --> 28:14.890
[to eliminate future threats.]

28:15.200 --> 28:15.750
Why?

28:16.810 --> 28:19.440
Why can Prince Duan
always predict my predictions?

28:19.440 --> 28:20.240
Could it be...

28:20.640 --> 28:22.370
-that when I think I’m at the very top,
-Greetings,

28:21.190 --> 28:25.130
[Ways to win over Deputy Commander Zhao]

28:22.550 --> 28:24.010
-Consort Yu.
-Prince Duan

28:24.270 --> 28:25.810
has already standing one level higher,
seeing the whole board?

28:25.810 --> 28:28.700
It can freely travel
between different worlds.

28:28.790 --> 28:30.070
That's much better.

28:30.200 --> 28:32.200
So his feigned ignorance before...

28:32.790 --> 28:34.120
was just a smokescreen.

28:34.880 --> 28:35.960
Can he see

28:36.270 --> 28:38.000
what happened tonight as well?

28:38.310 --> 28:40.640
We’re the real mice, toyed by Prince Duan.

28:41.830 --> 28:43.360
Could it be that in his eyes,

28:44.070 --> 28:46.030
I am a real 2D character?

29:06.960 --> 29:08.510
You said you'd stay with me
the whole time,

29:08.510 --> 29:10.240
but you left Xie Yong'er with me

29:10.350 --> 29:11.950
and came here to drink alone.

29:12.070 --> 29:12.550
Wanyin,

29:13.350 --> 29:14.480
you're unreliable.

29:17.590 --> 29:18.270
CEO Dan.

29:20.550 --> 29:21.410
We're done for.

29:22.480 --> 29:23.540
Why do you say that?

29:28.240 --> 29:30.110
Offer the Emperor the beauty
from the Qiang State.

29:28.810 --> 29:29.730
[Spread false information at the border,]

29:29.750 --> 29:30.260
[getting spies from other countries
to remove Li.]

29:30.260 --> 29:30.780
[The secret letter has been sent out.
Awaiting updates.]

29:31.030 --> 29:33.960
remove Li on charges of espionage.

29:34.550 --> 29:35.680
What does that mean?

29:35.720 --> 29:37.450
This is from the original book.

29:38.270 --> 29:39.000
But look at

29:40.240 --> 29:41.510
what Xu Yao wrote.

29:41.810 --> 29:43.260
[Spread false information at the border,]

29:42.030 --> 29:44.200
Spread false information at the border,

29:43.290 --> 29:44.800
[[getting spies from other countries
to remove Li.]]

29:44.800 --> 29:46.310
[The secret letter has been sent out.
Awaiting updates.]

29:44.830 --> 29:47.560
getting spies from other countries
to remove Li.

29:48.400 --> 29:50.530
It’s still about getting rid of Mr. Li,

29:50.750 --> 29:52.510
but Xiahou Bo’s method

29:53.160 --> 29:53.890
has changed.

29:55.510 --> 29:57.370
On the 15th night of the 1st month,

29:57.440 --> 29:59.370
by the golden willows by the river,

30:00.200 --> 30:02.400
bribe the son of Grand Tutor Wei,

30:03.270 --> 30:04.550
using a beauty

30:05.240 --> 30:06.750
to get the ledger.

30:07.510 --> 30:09.240
On the 12th night of the 1st month,

30:09.240 --> 30:12.000
report Grand Tutor Wei’s son
to the Court of Revision

30:12.000 --> 30:14.400
for obtaining the ledger through bribery.

30:15.310 --> 30:18.160
Kill the imperial censor's
secret guards in the backyard

30:18.160 --> 30:19.820
to eliminate future threats.

30:20.070 --> 30:22.880
Kill the imperial censor's
secret guards in the backyard

30:22.880 --> 30:24.240
to eliminate future threats.

30:24.240 --> 30:26.030
Without what happened today,

30:28.350 --> 30:29.270
I might

30:30.680 --> 30:32.110
never have noticed

30:32.110 --> 30:33.790
these subtle changes.

30:35.960 --> 30:37.400
Even if I had,

30:39.640 --> 30:42.170
I would’ve brushed them off
as faulty memory.

30:45.750 --> 30:46.240
CEO Dan,

30:47.510 --> 30:49.110
Prince Duan is a real person.

30:50.750 --> 30:52.590
And we, like Xie Yong'er,

30:53.160 --> 30:54.760
are just a few lines of words.

30:57.680 --> 30:58.830
Press delete,

31:00.480 --> 31:01.830
and we’re gone.

31:02.310 --> 31:03.110
So you mean...

31:04.920 --> 31:07.070
Xiahou Bo can predict our predictions,

31:07.070 --> 31:08.400
and he is the real person

31:08.960 --> 31:10.690
standing at the highest level?

31:11.030 --> 31:12.310
Exactly!

31:15.160 --> 31:15.750
So...

31:17.400 --> 31:18.460
you want to give up?

31:18.720 --> 31:20.580
Actually, I have another option.

31:21.270 --> 31:23.240
I can wave the white flag right now

31:24.110 --> 31:25.400
and defect to his side.

31:27.240 --> 31:27.920
Do you think

31:29.000 --> 31:30.240
he would take me in?

31:34.000 --> 31:34.590
No.

31:36.880 --> 31:37.960
He doesn't...

31:39.070 --> 31:40.030
need me at all.

31:41.270 --> 31:41.920
Maybe...

31:44.480 --> 31:46.680
you could make him fall in love with you.

31:49.550 --> 31:50.350
And then...

31:52.200 --> 31:53.550
take back

31:54.240 --> 31:56.570
the female lead script that belongs to me?

32:00.720 --> 32:01.590
Forget it.

32:03.550 --> 32:04.030
He...

32:04.920 --> 32:06.320
already has Xie Yong'er.

32:06.750 --> 32:07.790
Xie Yong'er can't compare to you.

32:07.340 --> 32:08.170
♪ Tell me ♪

32:08.880 --> 32:09.790
Of course.

32:08.880 --> 32:12.290
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

32:11.830 --> 32:12.350
So...

32:14.020 --> 32:15.080
♪ Walk past me ♪

32:15.480 --> 32:19.230
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

32:16.200 --> 32:17.660
do you want to give it a try?

32:20.490 --> 32:23.090
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

32:23.880 --> 32:26.660
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

32:27.390 --> 32:33.140
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

32:29.510 --> 32:31.510
I don't think I'm willing to do that.

32:34.330 --> 32:35.270
♪ Blame me ♪

32:36.050 --> 32:39.460
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

32:36.880 --> 32:37.310
Why?

32:38.030 --> 32:39.440
He is too scary.

32:40.590 --> 32:42.200
He could easily play mind games

32:41.150 --> 32:42.130
♪ Hide me ♪

32:42.650 --> 32:46.700
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

32:43.270 --> 32:46.030
to make me fall hopelessly
in love with him,

32:47.550 --> 32:49.440
then willingly

32:48.120 --> 32:50.380
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

32:50.590 --> 32:52.240
give everything for him,

32:51.300 --> 32:53.890
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

32:53.030 --> 32:54.680
throw myself in front of him

32:54.800 --> 32:57.760
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

32:56.400 --> 32:58.070
to block a blade

32:57.780 --> 32:59.940
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

32:59.240 --> 33:00.510
or an arrow,

33:00.340 --> 33:02.790
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

33:02.480 --> 33:04.550
and finally die in his arms,

33:02.840 --> 33:04.600
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

33:04.630 --> 33:07.150
♪ I never yielded ♪

33:05.790 --> 33:07.400
without any regrets.

33:07.460 --> 33:08.900
♪ But why ♪

33:08.720 --> 33:10.590
He’d casually shed a few tears,

33:09.190 --> 33:13.650
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

33:11.640 --> 33:13.240
give me a grand burial,

33:14.090 --> 33:16.410
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

33:15.550 --> 33:17.310
and then immediately go find Xie Yong'er.

33:16.500 --> 33:18.350
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

33:18.380 --> 33:20.700
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

33:19.550 --> 33:20.400
This...

33:21.120 --> 33:22.850
♪ The first time I met you ♪

33:21.680 --> 33:24.440
This is how men achieve great things.

33:23.250 --> 33:31.070
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

33:29.070 --> 33:29.550
Well...

33:33.000 --> 33:34.260
what about Xiahou Dan?

33:44.640 --> 33:47.930
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

33:50.270 --> 33:51.130
Your Highness!

33:52.030 --> 33:52.890
Your Highness!

33:53.830 --> 33:54.690
Your Highness!

33:54.850 --> 33:55.710
Your Highness!

33:56.590 --> 33:57.450
Your Highness.

33:59.550 --> 34:01.270
Noble Consort Yu's calligraphy works

34:01.270 --> 34:02.200
are truly hard to find.

34:02.200 --> 34:05.340
[Lyrics of Butterfly Love]

34:02.790 --> 34:04.200
In the entire Yu Residence,

34:04.200 --> 34:05.510
there isn't any.

34:06.420 --> 34:07.510
I spent

34:07.720 --> 34:09.000
a lot of effort

34:09.550 --> 34:10.280
and finally

34:10.550 --> 34:11.920
found this scrap of writing

34:11.920 --> 34:14.050
at her maternal grandfather’s place.

34:16.480 --> 34:17.739
Noble Consort Yu's...

34:18.360 --> 34:19.290
handwriting...

34:19.840 --> 34:20.900
is quite graceful.

34:21.630 --> 34:22.000
Yes.

34:24.110 --> 34:25.110
Where's that one?

34:26.880 --> 34:28.699
[Butterfly Love]

34:28.719 --> 34:29.600
[Colorful black, haha]

34:31.320 --> 34:32.320
What do you think?

34:34.800 --> 34:35.960
These two pieces...

34:37.110 --> 34:38.960
This one is a poem.

34:39.920 --> 34:41.030
While that one...

34:44.270 --> 34:49.920
[Colorful black, haha][Earth Element]

34:45.030 --> 34:46.000
Well...

34:47.630 --> 34:48.840
In my humble opinion,

34:50.110 --> 34:50.639
these...

34:50.800 --> 34:51.730
these two pieces

34:52.400 --> 34:54.800
don’t seem to be written
by the same person.

35:02.150 --> 35:04.150
It's time to meet her.
